Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running like a fugitive,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being chased by something
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside my heart is pounding
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My throat dry like it's withering
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.64,0:00:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For no single one,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To none does belong,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time is ours, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unraveling the pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unraveling our hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unraveling shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stifling our breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:00:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reaching for beyond,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tearing through the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fighting and in love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the distant light above,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.62,0:01:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we are on the way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rockin' my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon in the Snow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gatô, why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who are those henchmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our strategy has changed\Na little…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about this Zabuza,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you will die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since hiring a regular Shinobi\Ncosts a lot of money,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hired Rouge Ninjas like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, it would have been even\Nmore ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to save my money and effort if\NNinja-to-Ninja battles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ended in each killing the other off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you are certainly not worthy\Nof being called
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Demon of the\NHidden Mist Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to ask me,\Nyou're just a cute little demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many of them…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi…I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our fight ends here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as my reason to\Ntake down Tazuna is gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no reason to fight you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe him something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He squeezed my arm 'til it broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing, hey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Don't act so recklessly…!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say something, too!\NHe was your comrade, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, punk.\NHaku is already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel anything watching\Nhim doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you with Haku for a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Gatô used me…\NI was simply using Haku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd told you…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Shinobi are merely tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I wanted were his skills\Nand not Haku himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no regrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you...\NDo you really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to fight\Nhim anymore...  Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!\NMy enemy is still... this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really liked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there someone special in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He liked you that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a person feels he wants\Nto protect a person special to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that person can truly become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so,\Ndon't you feel anything at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult for me to completely\Nbecome a Shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really... honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't feel anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to make that person's\Ndream come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that, I could completely\Nbecome a Shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a person becomes\Nas strong as you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that person really\Nbehave like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He threw his life away\Nfor you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to make that\Nperson’s dream come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't even fulfill his\Nown dreams and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To die as a tool...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...\NThat's... too painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything... anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haku was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't just thinking of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was feeling pain inside\Nfor you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while he battled you guys too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. 					He was too kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we could fight with you\Nat the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, little punk,\Nit's as you say, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinobi are human too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's impossible to become\Nan emotionless tool...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Give me the Kunai knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Take them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can win by yourself\Nagainst this many of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so anxious\Nto join your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you go ahead... alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't... intend on going...\Nto the same place... as Haku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?! Pretending to be so tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to hell with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Demon of\Nthe Hidden Mists Village
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dies and goes to hell,\Nhe can become a real demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you find out\Nfor sure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if I'm a cute little demon or not in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... it's goodbye, Haku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end for\Na man who lived fiercely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I... die...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I... am I...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura, you're heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke, Sasuke, Sasuke...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura... 					That hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things turned out well,\N didn't they, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, you shouldn't move...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where's Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also,\Nwhat happened to that mask guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... the masked kid,\Nhe died...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Died? Did Naruto get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm not really sure,\Nbut he protected Zabuza...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are awesome, Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You avoided getting inflicted with\Nany mortal wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the beginning... he intended to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke's all right!\NHe's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was feeling pain inside\Nfor you while he battled you guys too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was too kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... He...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Sasuke's all right too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are too relaxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn Ninja...!\NKilling our source of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no choice but to attack\Nthe whole town and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take everything valuable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:12:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, this isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a Jutsu\Nto annihilate them all at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!\NI've used too much Chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemies who come any closer\Nto the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all the might of\Nall the island's people...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will not be allowed to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inari!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes always arrive\Non the scene late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inari... You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm gonna help out, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do that even\Nwith my scarce Chakra...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, it will bluff...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi Version!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... are you ready to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it’s over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi...\NI need to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His...\NI want to see his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow at this time\Nof the year...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haku... 					Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kakashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were always at my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can be at your side in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the same place...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was born in a village\Nwhere it snowed a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a boy as pure as snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be able to go, Zabuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you... together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, Kakashi Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the way a Ninja\Nshould be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is really as these\Ntwo were saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinobi should not seek\Nthe reason for their own existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is to\Nexist merely as tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same in the Land of Leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that's what\Nit really means
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to become a real Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... I guess...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think so, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... That's why all Ninja live
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,trying to figure that\Nout without realizing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Zabuza... and that kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pursue my\Nown Way of Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna sprint straight\Nahead and pursue
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a way that I absolutely\Nwon't regret!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you the bridge\Nwas safely completed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we will miss you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come back for\Na visit again, Tazuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For sure...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inari... you're gonna\Nmiss us, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right to cry.\NGo ahead and cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right if you cry,\NNaruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh....!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy changed Inari's mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Inari changed the minds\Nof the village people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy created a bridge\Nlinking us to hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a bridge called courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So a linking bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of bridges,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we need to name\Nthis bridge, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a perfect name\Nfor this bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Naruto Great Bridge?\NHow's that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll get back soon\Nand have Iruka Sensei treat me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to ramen as\Nthe mission completion celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And! And! I'll tell Konohamaru\Ntales of my heroic exploits!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sasuke, do you want to go\Non a date
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we get back to the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know! You know!\NI'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you sure\Nthat name's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This name is to wish that\Nthis bridge will never collapse...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And someday, it'll be the name\Nof a very famous bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A name heard around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's truly what I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.60,0:23:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Group Seven always\Nhas the easy missions lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, there are plenty of\Npowerful Ninja
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.60,0:23:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like Zabuza and Haku in other lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there more exciting missions\Nwhere I can be more active?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.37,0:23:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where I can use my Way of\Nthe Ninja and my soul like…you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.68,0:23:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:\N"A New Chapter Begins:\N		The Chunin Exam!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.08,0:23:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Way of Ninja!
